{"lemma":"بُورُ","slug":"بُورُ","root":"NTWS","root_slug":"NTWS","root_link":"/words/roots/NTWS","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun_prop","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"بُور","root":"بور","pos":"N","occurrence_count":2},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":5,"pos_tags":["adj","name","noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":7},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n3523"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A8%D9%8F%D9%88%D8%B1%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"fallow, uncultivated"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"stagnant, waste-"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to let lie fallow, to leave uncultivated, to leave unsown"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to make unprofitable, to make useless"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of بَارَ (bāra) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"name","gloss":"Bor (a city in South Sudan)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"synonym of مَرْفَأ (marfaʔ, “port, harbor”) used only in place names"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Compare بَارَ (bāra, “to lie fallow”).\n\nFrom French port."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n3523","headword_ar":"بُورٌ","root":"bwr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"A"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bad,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"corrupt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"man; (S, A, K;) and one (M, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a state of perdition;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, A, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in whom is no good;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;) originally an inf. n., (Fr, T,) and [therefore, as an epithet,] applied also to a female, (AO, T, S, M, K,) and to two persons, and more: (AO, T, M, K:) [but see what here follows:] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAy^irN","text_ar":"بَايِرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", also, signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bad,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"corrupt; destitute of good;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Zj, M;) a man"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a state of perdition;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AO, T, S;) and its pl., (K,) or rather quasi-pl., (M, TA,) is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baworN","text_ar":"بَوْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nawomN","text_ar":"نَوْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naAy^imN","text_ar":"نَايِمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SawomN","text_ar":"صَوْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaAy^imN","text_ar":"صَايِمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M, TA;) and another pl. of the same is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buwrN","text_ar":"بُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (AO, T, S, M,) like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuwlN","text_ar":"حُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAy^ilN","text_ar":"حَايِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or, accord. to some, as Akh states, this is a dial. var., not a pl., of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAy^irN","text_ar":"بَايِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baworN","text_ar":"بَوْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in three places.       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~ahumo lafiY HuwrK wa buwrK","text_ar":"اـِنَّهُمْ لَفِى حُورٍ وَ بُورٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA [but in the latter,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jwr","text_ar":"جور"},{"kind":"text","text":"is put for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hawr","text_ar":"حَور"},{"kind":"text","text":"])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily they are in a state of deficiency,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"detriment."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAy^irN","text_ar":"بَايِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". [And see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaworN","text_ar":"حَوْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ahaba fulaAnN fiY","text_ar":"ذَهَبَ فُلَانٌ فِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHawAri wa AlbawaAri","text_ar":"الحَوارِ وَ البَوَارِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one went away in a defective and bad state."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hwr","text_ar":"حور"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"}],"source_refs":["M","K","Fr","T","AO","S","TA"]}]}}